        "description": {
            "chat": "",
            "label": "Description",
            "type": "String",
            "unidentified": "",
            "value": "<p>Your hands become infused with positive energy, healing a living creature or damaging an undead creature with a touch. If you use lay on hands on a willing living target, you restore 6 Hit Points; if the target is one of your allies, they also gain a +2 status bonus to AC for 1 round. Against an undead target, you deal 1d6 damage and it must attempt a basic Fortitude save; if it fails, it also takes a -2 status penalty to AC for 1 round.</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Heightened (+1)</strong> The amount of healing increases by 6, and the damage to an undead target increases by 1d6.</p>"
